lexity of Public Engagement, in Nature Nanotechnology, ''[http://www.nature.com/nnano/journal/v7/n2/full/nnano.2012.5.html]'', February 2012.\n* Why Do We Need to Know What the Public Thinks about Nanotechnology? ''[https://www.springer.com/social+sciences/applied+ethics/journal/11569 NanoEthics]'', August 2009.\n* Piecing Together the Elephant: Public Engagement on Nanotechnology Challenges\u2019, ''[https://www.springer.com/social+sciences/applied+ethics/journal/11948 Science and Engineering Ethics]'', Volume 15 Number 3, 2009.\n* What do the Public Really Think and Who do they Really Trust, in  ''Human Biotechnology and Public Trust'', [http://fcms.its.utas.edu.au/law/law/facCentres.asp Centre for Law and Genetics, University of Tasmania], 2008.\n* Public Attitudes Towards GM Crops and Foods, ''[http://www.aiast.com.au/index.php?menu=publications&action=pub_argri_science Agricultural Science]'', Volume 21, No 2 \u2013 September 2007.\n* A clonagem vai ao cinema, Historia Ciencias Saude,  ''[http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_serial&pid=0104-5970&lng=en&nrm=iso Manghinhos]'', Brazil, Volume 13, October 2006.\n* Lies Deep Fries and Statistics,''[http://www.choicesmagazine.org/2005-4/GMOs/index.htm Choices]'', USA. 2005.\n* Perceptions of Risk Relating to Biotechnology in Australia, ''[http://www.inderscience.com/browse/index.php?issue=1/2/3&journalID=4&vol=7&year=2005 International Journal of Biotechnology]''. Vol 5, No 2, 2003.\n* Recent Changes in Public Attitudes Towards Biotechnology in Australia, ''[http://www.aibiol.org.au/news/journal/writing.html Australian Biologist]'', Vol.15 (2), September 2002.\n* Australian Attitudes to GM Foods and Crops, ''[http://pubs.rsc.org/en/journals/journalissues/po Pesticide Outlook]'', Royal Society of Chemistry, December 2002.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20111002064202/http://www.newholland.com.au/authordetail.php?first=Craig&last=Cormick&number=393 New Holland Publishers: Craig Cormick biography/photo]\n* [http://verityla.com/?s=Craig+Cormick&submit= Verity LA: An interview with Craig Cormick]\n* [http://www.abc.net.au/rn/arts/atbooks/s248412.htm ABC: Craig Cormick interview] with [[Margaret Throsby]]\n* [http://www.deakin.edu.au/research/admin/pubs/reports/database/dynamic/output/person/person.php?person_code=cormicr Deakin University: Research output for Craig Cormick]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20140708082533/http://upcoming4.me/news/book-news/the-story-behind-the-shadow-master-by-craig-cormick The story behind The Shadow Master \u2013 Essay by Craig Cormick] at Upcoming4.me\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cormick, Craig}}\n[[Category:Australian science writers]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Canberra]]\n[[Category:1961 births]]\n", "name_user": "Chris the speller", "label": "safe", "comment": "replaced: Books Published \u2192 Books published, Books Edited \u2192 Books edited,typo(s) fixed: the USA \u2192 the US, \u2019s \u2192 's", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Craig_Cormick"}
